snippet.title: Shenmue III Mood Video - Spirit Of The Land [DE]
snippet.description:
The latest Shenmue III trailer was just revealed at Tokyo Game Show 2019.

Feel the spirit of the land that Ryo will explore & discover in the third instalment of the Shenmue series.

Get ready to continue his adventure on November 19th, 2019.

#shenmueIII #ryohazuki #yusuzuki
